{"id":48330,"date":"2026-01-24T10:28:40","date_gmt":"2026-01-24T09:28:40","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.portugalrunning.com\/?post_type=ajde_events&#038;p=48330"},"modified":"2026-05-10T10:57:29","modified_gmt":"2026-05-10T09:57:29","slug":"grande-premio-internacional-de-viseu","status":"publish","type":"ajde_events","link":"https:\/\/www.portugalrunning.com\/eventos\/grande-premio-internacional-de-viseu\/","title":{"rendered":"Grande Pr\u00e9mio Internacional de Viseu 2026"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div style=\"font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; width: 100%; max-width: 1100px; margin: 20px auto;\">\n  \n  <h2 style=\"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 15px; border-left: 5px solid #eab308; padding-left: 15px;\">\n    Resultados\n  <\/h2>\n\n  <div style=\"border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\">\n    \n    <div style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a; padding: 15px 20px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px;\">\n      <div>\n        <span style=\"background: #eab308; color: #000; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;\">Live Results<\/span>\n        <h3 style=\"margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.5px;\">GPI Viseu 2026 &#8211; 10K<\/h3>\n      <\/div>\n      \n      <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 10px;\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/waitastart.com\/results26\/?r=gpi-viseu-2026_10K&#038;c=3&#038;g=1\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: #3b82f6; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; transition: all 0.2s ease; border: 1px solid #2563eb;\" rel=\"noopener\">\n           Abrir em Ecr\u00e3 Total \u2197\n        <\/a>\n      <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div style=\"width: 100%; height: 750px; background-color: #fff; position: relative;\">\n      <iframe \n        src=\"https:\/\/waitastart.com\/results26\/?r=gpi-viseu-2026_10K&#038;c=3&#038;g=1\" \n        width=\"100%\" \n        height=\"100%\" \n        frameborder=\"0\"\n        style=\"display: block;\"\n        allow=\"clipboard-write\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        title=\"Resultados Waitastart\">\n      <\/iframe>\n    <\/div>\n    \n    <div style=\"background: #f8fafc; padding: 10px 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #64748b;\">Cronometragem: <strong>Waitastart<\/strong><\/span>\n      <span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8;\">Os tempos s\u00e3o atualizados em tempo real<\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Uma prova com hist\u00f3ria e tradi\u00e7\u00e3o \u2013 64 anos a correr !<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Na manh\u00e3 de domingo de 10 de maio, os viseenses poder\u00e3o assistir e correr na 64\u00aa edi\u00e7\u00e3o do Grande Pr\u00e9mio Internacional \u201cCidade de Viseu\u201d, a mais antiga prova pedestre do nosso pa\u00eds e por aqui, passaram verdadeiras lendas da modalidade.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Um percurso de 10k para seniores e veteranos, partida \u00e0s 10h15.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>O GPI cidade de Viseu \u00e9 promovido pela Associa\u00e7\u00e3o de Atletismo de Viseu com a gest\u00e3o t\u00e9cnica da NativeWarriors.pt<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":48331,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"zakra_general_container_width":0,"zakra_general_content_width":0,"zakra_general_sidebar_width":0,"zakra_sticky_header":"customizer","zakra_header_main_area":true,"zakra_site_logo_width":0,"zakra_header_top_enabled":"customizer","zakra_header_top_style":"customizer","zakra_primary_menu_item_style":"customizer","zakra_page_header_text_color":"","zakra_page_header_layout":"customizer","zakra_page_title_bg":"","z